description:
A homebrew visual novel for the Sega Genesis

What if it turns out that your girlfriend likes girls? It's very simple, find a nice partner for her. You can become a real Casanova and entice a bunch of girls. The goal of this game is very clear. The game consists of two parts: an interactive comic and an arcade part.

Features:
30+ backgrounds;
Action mini-game;
4 girls;
Many ends;
6 music tracks;
